	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De <placeName ref="l491">Argentinensibus</placeName> multa feruntur absurda, quę lubens praetereo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Legi literas 6. Septembris datas, in quibus hęc inerant: concionatores nihil sui officii praetermittere atque sic perstituros; deinde adhuc spem esse, eo quod adhuc semel referenda sit res ad concilium magnum; Cęsarem quoque vix permissurum, quę ab ipsis petantur; tum ergo cognitum iri, quid sit in animo; pręterea eundem properare praeter expectationem omnium in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808">Belgas</placeName>, sive quod advenerit filius, sive quod aliquid motum sit illic.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Qua de re spargitur nonnihil, sed incertum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tria rumor circum fert:</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">1. esse civitatem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l631">Burgundicam</placeName> in confiniis regni <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Francici</placeName>; eo missos inquisitores, et qui inventi sint Lutherani, male tractatos; concurrisse itaque cives et occidisse omnes sacerdotes Baales, papales dico, et sese devovisse <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832">Gall.</placeName></s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">2. Bis milites adversarios duce comite a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l1716">Mansfelden</placeName> fusos; reginam <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l882">Ungarię</placeName> sic turbatam, ut fugientem in quoddam monasterium mors sit sequuta.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">3. <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l168">Gandavum</placeName> receptum a suis idque hoc pacto; Gubernator, qui fuit in arce nova extructa ab imperatore, mortem obiit.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Convenit ingens civium multitudo ad funus atque, dum arx fuit aperta, cives irruperunt et occuparunt literis protinus scriptis ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p20225">Gallum</persName>, ut facinus tueatur.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">His igitur tam diu fruaris, dum alia supervenient, quibus certius instrueris.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Es hand die <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l267">Cölnischen</placeName> schifflüt geseyt, si habint dem kaiser gfuͤrt büchsen etc. nünmal hundert tusig centner.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Serium est, quod virum urget, quicquid sit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p1278">Gastius</persName> se misisse ait, quę toties petisti.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale fortis in domino, qui solus fortes efficit ac constantes.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l28">Basileę</placeName> 13. Septembris anno 1548.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salvi sint <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8171">Theodorus</persName>, <persName ref="p8127">Pellicanus</persName>, <persName ref="p8011">Gvaltherus</persName>, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8459">Otto</persName> in Christo Iesu.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8418">Os[valdus] Myc[onius</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, ministro Christi fortissimo, domino in Christo suo.</s>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="de" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="citizen_name">Zürich</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
